sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    participant User as User
    participant GE_UI as Gemini Enterprise
    participant Agent as InsightComparator
    participant Tool as compare_insights
    participant DE as Discovery Engine
    participant STS as Google STS
    participant SPO as SharePoint
    participant Gemini as Gemini Model
    participant Google as Google Search

    User->>GE_UI: "Compare our policy with industry"

    Note over GE_UI: User authorized agent<br/>Token in state: temp:sharepointauth2

    GE_UI->>Agent: Invoke with message
    Agent->>Agent: Detect auth key in state
    Agent->>Tool: compare_insights(query, context)

    Note over Tool: Extract MS JWT from<br/>tool_context.state

    par Internal Search
        Tool->>STS: Exchange JWT
        STS-->>Tool: GCP Token
        Tool->>DE: streamAssist + dataStoreSpecs
        DE->>SPO: Query with user identity
        SPO-->>DE: ACL-filtered docs
        DE-->>Tool: SharePoint findings
    and External Search
        Tool->>Gemini: Generate with googleSearch
        Gemini->>Google: Web search
        Google-->>Gemini: Results
        Gemini-->>Tool: Web findings
    end

    Tool-->>Agent: Internal + External findings
    Agent->>Agent: Synthesize comparison
    Agent-->>GE_UI: Formatted response
    GE_UI-->>User: Display comparison
